						               													<description>Tired of hanging out with people who are distracted by their phones?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Once you&amp;rsquo;ve reached adulthood, meeting up with friends becomes extra challenging. It&amp;rsquo;s hard to get everyone&amp;rsquo;s schedule to synchronize.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When you finally get the chance to meet, it&amp;rsquo;s best to savor the moment and just enjoy each other&amp;rsquo;s company. But even this has been made difficult by people&amp;rsquo;s addiction to their screens. We all tend to frequently check our phone on impulse.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Trivia Drinking Card Game by DrinkQuizition create fun moments, gadget-free!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The best new card game from DRNK Games, DrinkQuizition brings memorable times to people by marrying together our love for beer and trivia. Pop a bottle and get ready to prove your superior knowledge in pop culture, history, entertainment and more! Your phone will never cross your mind as you get engrossed in the fun game and friendly banter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;No person is too drunk to understand our easy-to-follow card game. Simply pick a card from the top of the deck then answer the indicated question. You get to keep the card if your answer is correct, and you&amp;rsquo;ll have to drink for every mistake. The person with the most cards wins the game! Our DrinkQuizition cards are divided into the &amp;ldquo;Common Knowledge&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Trivia&amp;rdquo; deck, each with 30 questions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Our game comes with fun twists! Every time you get an answer wrong, someone else can steal your card by calling out the correct answer. You may also use the &amp;ldquo;Bonus Questions&amp;rdquo; to save yourself. The caveat is that you will have to take two drinks if you get it wrong.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Here are more reasons to love our drinking card game:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#156;&amp;#133; A fresh new take on game nights&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#156;&amp;#133; Appeals to the thinking person&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#156;&amp;#133; Learning experience through the &amp;ldquo;Fun Facts&amp;rdquo; feature&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
